item.title: CVE-2023-26132|2023-06-10T05:00:01.826Z -- n%2Fa -- dottie
item.description: Versions of the package dottie before 2.0.4 are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution due to insufficient checks, via the set() function and the current variable in the /dottie.js file.
